Token_v2 and several others
The use of these Reddit cookies is to enable to track if the visitor comes from the Reddit webpage and which actions are taken after being redirected. Also, they might retain the credentials.
Reddit Pixel.js
The Reddit pixel is used to enable advertising on their website and to track behavior of the visitor after selecting the advertisement.
